Zm_stab_smugglersdust_v2a
---------------------------------
http://www.zmmapperz.net
---------------------------------

made by Stabhappyjim (stabby@zmmapperz.net)
betatesting/debugging by Alex/Terrora

This map was inspired by zm_cbble_b3 so it has lots of camping spots on boxes
but i also added some indoor areas where you can build barricades.
I tried to make this map as balanced as possible and force zombies/humans
to work as team to hold a spot.

Features
- 50+ spawns
- Barricade spots
- Camping spots
- 5 secrets
- Custom textures


Originally i made this map for Zombienetwork.Net gameservers
but now i see other servers are using this map too
so i might as well release it for everyone.
In the archive is the BSP as well as a bzipped on for your fastDL mirror

Its been on a couple of servers already including our own.
and it has good FPS even on full server of 40 people.

i hope you like this map :)

for more maps by our members please visit our 
zombiemod servers/mapping community at 

http://www.zmmapperz.net
